setting.activity: This recording takes place at the family's home, at Clermont-Ferrand, and more precisely in the child's bedroom. At the beginning, the child and her father play and discuss various topics, especially about what the child does at school. Then, the mother comes and everybody go to the kitchen to have lunch. Everybody talk discuss various topics. We note that there are a lot of discussions between the parents in wich the childtries to participate.
